physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Patient diagnosed with bilateral renal cysts and hypertension; developed bilateral chromophobe renal cell carcinoma; multiple benign renal cysts in transplanted kidney; the largest cyst was 2 cm in diameter.
physical_examinations.changes_over_time: In 2013, creatinine levels increased and ultrasonography showed multiple benign renal cysts in the transplanted kidney. In 2015, additional cysts developed.
